A software that handles only what they need, excluding all the extra buttons. Curi is a light weight, yet powerful, point of sale and inventory management software that makes the point of sale experience fast, easy and to- the - point. Enjoy :
- Offline transaction processing
- Credit card payments
- Kitchen screen.
- 24/7 tech support.
descriptionShort: A point of sale solution for retailers and food service merchants
